      <title>基础数论一</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/03/%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/03/%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>下面先给出一些基本定义及其符号表示</p><ul><li><p><strong>整除</strong>: 记 $ a|b $ 为 $ b $ 可以被 $ a $ 整除。即$q$, 使得 $ b = aq $。且称 <span class="math inline">\(a\)</span> 为<span class="math inline">\(b\)</span> 的约数, <spanclass="math inline">\(a\)</span> 为 <spanclass="math inline">\(b\)</span> 的倍数。</p></li><li><p><strong>带余除法(欧几里得除法)</strong>: 对于一个被除数 <spanclass="math inline">\(a\)</span> 和一个除数 <spanclass="math inline">\(b\)</span>, 有一个整数 <spanclass="math inline">\(p\)</span> 和一个介于一定范围的余数 <spanclass="math inline">\(r\)</span> ，使得 <span class="math inline">\(a =bq + r\)</span> 等式成立。<span class="math inline">\(a|b\)</span>等价于 <span class="math inline">\(a|r\)</span>。</p></li><li><p><strong>同余</strong>: 对于两个整数除以同一个正整数时,若得到的余数相同, 记为<span class="math inline">\(p\)</span>,则称这两个数在模 <span class="math inline">\(p\)</span> 意义下同余, 记作<span class="math inline">\(a \equiv b(mod p)\)</span>。</p></li><li><p><strong>素数(质数)</strong>: 在大于1的自然数中,只能被1和它本身整除而不能被其他数整除的数, 反之则为合数, 特别地,规定1不属于素数也不属于合数。</p></li><li><p><strong>最大公约数和最小公倍数</strong>: 最大公约数记为 <spanclass="math inline">\(gcd\)</span>, 最小公倍数记为 <spanclass="math inline">\(lcm\)</span>。特别地有 <spanclass="math inline">\(lcm(a, b) = \frac{a*b}{gcd(a,b)}\)</span>。</p></li><li><p><strong>互素(互质)</strong>: 若 <spanclass="math inline">\(gcd(a, b) = 1\)</span>, 则称 <spanclass="math inline">\(a\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(b\)</span> 互素, 同样地, 若有 <spanclass="math inline">\(gcd(a_1, a_2, a_3,..., a_n) = 1\)</span>, 则称<span class="math inline">\(a_1, a_2, a_3,..., a_n\)</span>互素。</p></li></ul><p>下面再给出一些基本定理(附简要证明) &gt; ###算数基本定理(正整数的唯一分解定理) <span class="math display">\[\forallA\in N,A&gt;1,\exist\prod^n_{i=1}p_i^{a_i}=A,p_1&lt;p_2&lt;...&lt;p_n\]</span> 其中 <spanclass="math inline">\(p_i\)</span> 是<strong>质数</strong>, 且 <spanclass="math inline">\(a_i\in\Zeta^+\)</span>这样的表示是<strong>存在且唯一</strong>的</p><p>下面利用反证法给出简单证明:</p><p>首先给出下面两个定理 <strong>最小数定理:</strong> 设 <spanclass="math inline">\(N\)</span> 是全体自然数组成的集合，<spanclass="math inline">\(M\)</span> 是 <spanclass="math inline">\(N\)</span> 的一个非空子集，则 <spanclass="math inline">\(M\)</span> 中必有最小数。<strong>欧几里得引理:</strong> 对于正整数 <span class="math inline">\(p,a, b\)</span>, 若有 <span class="math display">\[p|ab\ \ 且 \ \p是质数\]</span> 那么 <span class="math display">\[p|a \ 或 \p|b\]</span> <strong>存在性证明:</strong> 首先对于一切的质数,该定理显然满足。</p><p>假设存在不能分解成有限个质数乘积的合数集合, 则由最小数定理,其中必然有一个最小的合数 <span class="math inline">\(x\)</span>,又由合数定义可以得到 <spanclass="math inline">\(\mathbf{x=ab}\)</span>(其中 <spanclass="math inline">\(1&lt;a\le b&lt;x\)</span>)</p><p>1、假设 <span class="math inline">\(a, b\)</span> 都是质数,与假设矛盾 2、假设存在 <span class="math inline">\(a\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(b\)</span> 中存在合数, 而这个合数小于 <spanclass="math inline">\(x\)</span>, 故可以将该合数分解为有限个质数的乘积,替换到 <span class="math inline">\(x=ab\)</span>里, 发现 <spanclass="math inline">\(x\)</span> 也可以表示为有限个质数的乘积,与题设矛盾。 <strong>唯一性证明:</strong>假设存在可以分解为两组不同约数系的正整数, 则存在一个最小的正整数记为<span class="math inline">\(x\)</span> , 假设 <spanclass="math display">\[x=p_1p_2p_3\cdots p_s=q_1q_2q_3\cdotsq_r\]</span> 其中 <span class="math display">\[p_1\le p_2\le p_3\cdots\le p_s\quad q_1\le q_2\le q_3\cdots \le q_r\]</span> 不妨设 <spanclass="math inline">\(p_1 \le q_1\)</span></p><p>这里的等号是不成立的, 否则 <spanclass="math inline">\(x/p_1(x/q_1)\)</span> 就是一个更小的数,这与假设矛盾, 因此有 <span class="math inline">\(p_1 &lt; q_1 \le q_i(2\le i \le r)\)</span></p><p>由欧几里得引理 <spanclass="math display">\[p_1|q_1q_2q_3...q_n\]</span> 即在 <spanclass="math inline">\(q_1q_2q_3...q_n\)</span> 中存在 <spanclass="math inline">\(q_i\)</span> 使得 <spanclass="math inline">\(q_i\)</span> 能被 <spanclass="math inline">\(p_1\)</span> 整除, 又因为 <spanclass="math inline">\(p_1\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(q_i\)</span> 都是质数, 所以 <spanclass="math inline">\(p_1=q_i\)</span>, 与上述证明矛盾。 证毕。</p><p><em>试除法求约数 Code</em> <figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unordered_map&lt;<span class="type">int</span>, <span class="type">int</span>&gt;mp;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> x; cin &gt;&gt; x;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> j = <span class="number">2</span>; j &lt;= x / j; j++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(x % j == <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        mp[j]++;</span><br><span class="line">        x /= j;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(x &gt; <span class="number">1</span>) mp[x]++;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">auto</span> &amp;[p, a]: mp) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; q &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; s &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="裴蜀定理贝祖定理">裴蜀定理(贝祖定理)</h3><p>设 <span class="math inline">\(a, b\)</span> 是不全为 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 的整数, 则存在整数 <spanclass="math inline">\(x, y\)</span>, 使得 <spanclass="math display">\[ax + by = gcd(a, b)\]</span></p><p>对于不定方程 <span class="math inline">\(ax+by=m\)</span> , 当且仅当<span class="math inline">\(gcd(a, b)|m\)</span> 时有解,并且有解时有无穷多组解。</p><p>证明(辗转相除法): 1、若其中任意一个等于 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span>, 则有 <spanclass="math inline">\(gcd(a, b)=a(b)\)</span>, 此时结论显然成立。2、<span class="math inline">\(a, b\)</span> 都不为 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span>, 由于 <spanclass="math inline">\(gcd(a, b)=gcd(-a, b)\)</span>, 不妨设 <spanclass="math inline">\(a, b\)</span> 都大于 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span>, 且 <span class="math inline">\(b \lea\)</span> 。 令 <span class="math inline">\(gcd(a, b) = d\)</span>对上式两边同时除以 <span class="math inline">\(d\)</span> , 进而转证<span class="math display">\[a_1x+b_1y=1\]</span> 其中 <spanclass="math inline">\(gcd(a_1, b_1)=1\)</span> 由带余除法 <spanclass="math display">\[% \begin{equation}1.\quad a_1=q_1b+r_1\quad (0\le r_1&lt;b_1)\\2. \quad b_1=q_2r_1+r_2\quad (0\le r_2&lt;r_1)\\3. \quad r_1=q_3r_2+r_3\quad (0\le r_3&lt;r_2) \\\cdots \cdots \\4. \quad r_{n-4}=q_{n-2}r_{n-3}+r_{n-2} \\5. \quad r_{n-3}=q_{n-1}r_{n-2}+r_{n-1} \\6. \quad r_{n-2}=q_nr_{n-1}+r_n \\7. \quad r_{n-1}=q_{n+1}r_n+1 \\% \end{equation}\]</span><!-- $\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad 1.\quad a_1=q_1b+r_1\quad (0\le r_1<b_1)$$\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad 2. \quad b_1=q_2r_1+r_2\quad (0\le r_2<r_1)$$\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad 3. \quad r_1=q_3r_2+r_3\quad (0\le r_3<r_2)$$\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad ......$$\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad 4. \quad r_{n-4}=q_{n-2}r_{n-3}+r_{n-2}$$\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad 5. \quad r_{n-3}=q_{n-1}r_{n-2}+r_{n-1}$$\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad 6. \quad r_{n-2}=q_nr_{n-1}+r_n$$\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad\quad 7. \quad r_{n-1}=q_{n+1}r_n+1$ --></p><p>由 <span class="math inline">\(7\)</span> 式和 <spanclass="math inline">\(6\)</span> 式可推出 <spanclass="math display">\[r_{n-2}A_{n-2} + r_{n-1}B_{n-1} = 1\]</span> 结合<span class="math inline">\(5\)</span> <spanclass="math display">\[r_{n-3}A_{n-3} + r_{n-2}B_{n-2} = 1\]</span> 结合<span class="math inline">\(4\)</span> <spanclass="math display">\[r_{n-4}A_{n-4} + r_{n-3}B_{n-3} = 1\]</span><span class="math display">\[......\]</span> 结合 <spanclass="math inline">\(2\)</span> <span class="math display">\[b_1A_0 +r_1B_0 = 1\]</span> 最后结合 <span class="math inline">\(1\)</span><span class="math display">\[a_1x + b_1y = 1\]</span> 证毕。 同时,裴蜀定理在 <span class="math inline">\(n\)</span>个元素中也是成立的。</p><h3 id="扩展欧几里得算法">扩展欧几里得算法</h3><p>若要求 <span class="math inline">\(ax+by=gcd(a, b)\)</span>的一组解。</p><p>在普通欧几里得算法求 <span class="math inline">\(gcd\)</span>的过程中, 通常利用辗转相除法将求 <span class="math inline">\(gcd(a,b)\)</span> 的问题转化为求 <span class="math inline">\(gcd(b,a\%b)\)</span>, 而当递归到终点即 <span class="math inline">\(gcd(gcd,0)\)</span> 时, 显然有 <span class="math display">\[a \times 1 + b\times 0 = gcd\]</span> 考虑回推 当求 <span class="math inline">\(gcd(a,b)\)</span> 和 <span class="math inline">\(gcd(b, a\%b)\)</span>时有<span class="math display">\[ax_1+by_1=bx_2+(a\%b)y_2=gcd(a, b)\]</span>又考虑到 <span class="math display">\[a\%b=a-\lfloor \frac{a}{b} \rfloorb\]</span> 因此有 <spanclass="math display">\[ax_1+by_1=ay_1+b(x_2-\frac{a}{b}y_2)\]</span>整理后可以得到 <span class="math display">\[\begin{equation}\left\{    \begin{array}{ll}        x_1=y_2 \\        y_1=x_2-\frac{a}{b}y_2    \end{array}\right.\end{equation}\]</span></p><p><em>扩展欧几里得 Code</em> <figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> i64 = <span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">exgcd</span><span class="params">(i64 a, i64 b, i64 &amp;x, i64 &amp;y)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(!b)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        x = <span class="number">1</span>, y = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> a;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">exgcd</span>(b, a % b, y, x);</span><br><span class="line">    y -= a / b * x;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="费马小定理">费马小定理</h3><p>若 <span class="math inline">\(p\)</span> 为<strong>素数</strong>,<span class="math inline">\(gcd(a, p)=1\)</span>, 则 <spanclass="math inline">\(a^{p-1}\equiv 1(\%p)\)</span></p><p>特别地, 虽然所有的素数都满足该性质, 但并非合数就不满足该性质,有一类满足该性质的合数被成为卡迈克尔数, 也被成为伪素数。</p><p>在<strong>Korselt定理</strong>中首次给出了卡迈克尔数的等价定义:一个正合数 <span class="math inline">\(n\)</span> 是卡迈克尔数, 当且仅当<span class="math inline">\(n\)</span> 无平方数因数且对于所有 <spanclass="math inline">\(n\)</span> 的质因数 <spanclass="math inline">\(p\)</span> , 且 <spanclass="math inline">\(p-1|n-1\)</span> 。这个定理说明了所有卡迈克尔数都是奇数。</p><p>本定理证明略</p>]]></content>
      
      
